scientists have discovered a new species of extinct pygmy sperm whale , called nanokogia isthmia , which clarifies key aspects of the evolution of these animals . the well-preserved skulls of two individuals were unearthed at a sea cliff along the caribbean coast of panama . the remains indicate that the organ involved in sound generation and echolocation got smaller throughout the whale 's evolution .
