michigan micro mote is the smallest computer in the world , measuring less than 2mm across . it contains solar cells that power the battery with ambient light , including indoor rooms with no natural sunlight . the operator is able to send the information to a central computer via conventional radio frequencies . it is the first complete computer system measuring as small as two millimeters across .
